## 4. Notes & next steps

- Rollback this run: `./setup.sh --rollback {{ report_backup_stamp }}`
- Verify: `./verify-olvm-ha.sh --full`
- The VDSM `[vars]` keys (`heartbeat_interval`, `host_monitor_timeout`,
  `migration_timeout`) and the HA `agent.conf` keys beyond `monitoring_interval`
  should be confirmed against the daemon schema on a real system — unknown keys
  may be silently ignored (see REVIEW notes).
- `dev_loss_tmo infinity` in the multipath `overrides` block applies globally.
  In a Dell EMC ME5 (ALUA) environment, consider the ME5-scoped `device {}`
  option (`multipath_me5_device_block: true`).

